
[1]pantaloon

   PANTALOON', n.

   1. A garment for males in which breeches and stockings are in a piece;
   a species of close long trowsers extending to the heels.

   2. A character in the Italian comedy,and a buffoon in pantomimes; so
   called from his close dress.
